STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Robert S. BARTLEY, Defendant-Petitioner. C-118 September Term 2018
081106 Supreme Court of New Jersey. September 28, 2018.

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000916-17 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
